    • Constructor Detail

      • User

        public User​(java.lang.String username,
            Password password)
        Two-argument constructor. The two instance variables are initialized to the two arguments, ArrayLists of stories, subscriptions, friends, reports and services are initialized to empty ArrayLists. Boolean field of professional is initialized to false and the String fields of phone number and email are initialized to null values.
        Parameters:
        username - a String represent the User's alias
        password - a Password object to allow the user access to the system
        Throws:
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - - Username must have at least 3 characters
